{"tid":1626670,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"<澄清> <有圖>真•黃絲店","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:12.000Z","uid":178726,"like":14,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"916c1bff3b39d37b4e0d710770f0ed7e6c0fc739","tid":1626670,"uid":178726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LC42bgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLC42bgT.png&h=187d1dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依間野係我朋友個兄弟開<br />\n佢係黃到仆街<br />\n引用番我朋友個句 佢係黃到啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係藍絲惡意中傷<br />\n所以我幫佢澄清番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再推格離post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCggfJC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCggfJC.png&h=8292ee20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9916304747d75c5ba0bf3e1c7cd1f7052fc265d1","tid":1626670,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"請支持行動post<br />\n<br />\n【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"a36f30c425cfaf9d2af43aed5b2bd93e46c42ee1","tid":1626670,"uid":178726,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rO5Qkeg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrO5Qkeg.jpg&h=142